From 02058894db4d6cae4de44b38fcc3d0cef34b3047 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Danius Kalvaitis <danius@kurokesu.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 10:27:10 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] ipa: nxp: neo: Add IMX462 tuning data

Add initial tuning file for Sony IMX462 enabling AWB, BLC, AGC, CCM,
DRC (copy mode) and gamma. CCM table is from Raspberry Pi IMX462
calibration until we produce our own.

Add separate mono file for IMX462LLR without colour algorithms, using
the "_mono" suffix from Raspberry Pi tuning naming.

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [NXP libcamera fork specific]
